      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: C) II</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p>II represents the condenser. It is located beneath the stage, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fefa53d9f216927772037e31a651d7\">focusing</span> light onto the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c02ad9ae0f1692777198d76afc93c4\">specimen</span> for better resolution and contrast. It has an adjustment <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a7cd9d8dfb16927771902eebe8334c\">knob</span> for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fefa53d9f216927772037e31a651d7\">focusing</span> the light beam.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>I represents the Objective Lens</li>\n\t<li>III represents the stage</li>\n\t<li>IV represents the Small Knob</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Part of the Light Microscope </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Function </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Source of Illumination</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Visible Light</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Stage</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Slides are placed on it</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Condenser</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Regulates the passage of light</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Big Knob</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Coarse adjustment</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Small Knob</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Fine adjustment</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Eyepiece Lens</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>10x magnification</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Objective Lens</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Scanner: 4x</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Low Power: 10x</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>High Power: 40x</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Oil Immersion: 100x</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Â </p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Ann 2000\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY SA 4.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Ukrainian_microscope_(cropped).jpg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"378\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/ZndjaJWfNQydbKZIgCxC1745496867.png\" width=\"500\" />\n<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/QxBe5Me1ql90DFvkCLIA1745496877.png\" width=\"400\" /></p>",
